      .col-xs-12.col-sm-5.col-lg-3
        .page-title
          %h5.white-color.title.wow.fadeInUp{ data: { wow: { delay: '0.2s' } } }
            Screenshots

          .space-10
          %h3.white-color.wow.fadeInUp{ data: { wow: { delay: '0.4s' } } }
            Fully Featured App

        .space-20
        %div.desc.wow.fadeInUp{ data: { wow: { delay: '0.6s' } } }
          %p
            The Radio Spirits App Premium Plan allows you to search for, listen to and download thousands of classic radio programs. It also provides interesting background information on the shows and program stars.

        .space-50
        %a.bttn-default.wow.fadeInUp.downloadbutton{ href: "#download_page", data: { wow: { delay: '0.8s' } } }
          Download Free App

